# {{agent_name}} Agent

This agent was created using the Agent Foundry CLI.

## Setup

1. Make sure you have an OpenAI API key
2. Edit the `.env` file and set your `OPENAI_API_KEY`

## Usage

To start a chat session with this agent:

```bash
foundry run {{agent_name_lower}}
```

To send a single task/message to the agent:

```bash
foundry run {{agent_name_lower}} --task "Your message here"
```

